data.description: New on the market for sale. Must see won't last! 4 bedroom, 3 full bath townhouse in Cali Greens, an exclusive Keys Gate Community. Chandeliers in kitchen & dining, updated black granite sink w/black copper faucet. The owners added a fully finished closet in the stairwell w/lighting to take advantage of additonal storage. Ceiling fans in living room & all bedrooms convey. Proffessional blinds installed in all bedrooms & living room. Beautiful taupe, professionally installed curtains in living & dining rooms add a touch of elegance. One good size bedroom is conveniently located downstairs. Bedrooms are carpeted while other living spaces are 18x18 tile. Wood cabinets in kitchen w/stainless steel appliances. Updated washer & dryer w/steam. This home features hurricane windows, doors & garage.
